data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after Antelope Hills neighborhood of Bennett, Colorado! This magnificent 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom house, situated on a sprawling one-acre lot, offers the perfect blend of luxury and tranquility. As you step inside, the grandeur of this home is instantly evident with its soaring vaulted ceilings, setting a tone of spaciousness and elegance. The heart of this residence is undoubtedly the completely remodeled kitchen which features beautiful granite countertops, new cabinets, a double oven, and even includes a convenient pot filler – an absolute delight for any home chef. Adjacent to the kitchen is a full walk-in pantry which provides plenty of storage for all your kitchen essentials and groceries. Safety and security are also paramount as this home is equipped with a comprehensive closed-circuit surveillance system as well as a smart doorbell, providing peace of mind for you and your loved ones. In addition to modern amenities, the house boasts radiant in-floor heating, ensuring comfort and efficiency throughout the year. Retreat to the primary bedroom, where you'll find a luxurious 5-piece bathroom that will make your daily routine feel like a spa experience. A deep soaking tub, a separate shower, and dual vanities create a serene atmosphere for relaxation. Downstairs you'll find a temperature-controlled wine room, offering the ideal environment to store and showcase your wine collection. The outdoor space is a true oasis, showcasing a backyard that is a nature lover's paradise. Get the fire pit going then relax under your new gazebo while enjoying the sounds of the flowing water from your fountain, creating a little creek that meanders into a private pond. In this picturesque setting, you'll have the best of both worlds – a beautifully updated, modern home with the tranquility and space of country living. Schedule your tour today!
